name: The Garden Online: Educational Gaming for the Classroom
blurb: Video games in school: the new way to engage students! Help us develop a skill-building, writing-based MMORPG for the classroom!

rewards.reward: Early Bird =============================                                                                                                                                                 \r\n\u25cf The first 25 people to donate $5.00 will be able to name an NPC (Non-Player Character) in The Garden Online!
